cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with extracting a controllable model from a video and generating novel image sequences. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper discusses generating video with arbitrary backgrounds and capturing both dynamics and appearance of a person. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the method is based on two neural networks. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating novel video sequences based on user-defined control signals. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating video sequences of dancers and athletes.
